<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcf5fb540-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0" identifier="/us/usc/t48/s733a"><num value="733a">§ 733a.</num><heading> Citizens; residence in island of citizens of United States</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All citizens of the United States who have resided or who shall after <date date="1927-03-04">March 4, 1927</date>, reside in the island for one year shall be citizens of Puerto Rico.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcf5fb541-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0">(<ref href="/us/act/1917-03-02/ch145/s5a">Mar. 2, 1917, ch. 145, § 5a</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/act/1927-03-04/ch503/s2">Mar. 4, 1927, ch. 503, § 2</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/1418">44 Stat. 1418</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/act/1932-05-17/ch190">May 17, 1932, ch. 190</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/47/158">47 Stat. 158</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idcf5fb542-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idcf5fb543-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idcf5fb544-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t8/s5a">section 5a of Title 8</ref>, Aliens and Nationality.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idcf5fb545-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I78" topic="changeOfName" id="idcf5fb546-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Change of Name</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">“Puerto Rico” substituted in text for “Porto Rico” pursuant to act <date date="1932-05-17">May 17, 1932</date>, which is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t48/s731a">section 731a of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
